headline: Jacobs Supports Landmark Marselis Tunnel Project in Denmark
summary: Jacobs (NYSE: J) has been selected to support the design and management of the Marselis Tunnel, a central component of Denmark's Infrastructure Plan 2035 being delivered by the Danish Road Directorate in Aarhus.
